annotationA: Lethal (1) G0007, isoform A; ATP binding; ATP-dependent helicase activity; ATP-dependent RNA helicase activity; nucleic acid binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: regulation of alternative mRNA splicing, via spliceosome; imaginal disc-derived wing morphogenesis; mRNA splicing, via spliceosome; inter-male aggressive behavior
annotationB: Probable U2 small nuclear ribonucleoprotein A; U2A is a protein component of the U2 snRNP. The U2 snRNP combines with other snRNPs on the pre-mRNA to assemble a spliceosome
